TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Extracts the data from sql server sources
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_EVENT_HEADER

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT A.CUSTOMER_GROUP, B.ITEM_CODE, D.ORG_QTY, D.PRIOR_SHIPPED_QTY, D.SHIPPED_QTY, D.REMAINING_QTY, (SELECT FISCAL_YEAR_PERIOD FROM dbo.FISCAL_MONTH_CALENDAR WITH (nolock) WHERE SHIP_DATE BETWEEN MONTH_BEGIN_DATE AND MONTH_END_DATE) as FISCAL_YEAR_PERIOD, A.EVENT_HEADER_ID, A.DESCRIPTION, F.OWNER_NAME, A.EVENT_TYPE_CODE FROM dbo.EVENT_HEADER A WITH (nolock) LEFT JOIN dbo.EVENT_ITEMS B WITH (nolock) ON A.EVENT_HEADER_ID = B.EVENT_HEADER_ID LEFT JOIN dbo.EVENT_QUANTITIES D WITH (nolock) ON B.EVENT_ITEM_ID = D.EVENT_ITEM_ID LEFT JOIN dbo.EVENT_BUCKETS E WITH (nolock) ON D.EVENT_BUCKET_ID = E.EVENT_BUCKET_ID LEFT JOIN dbo.EVENT_OWNERS F WITH (nolock) ON A.EVENT_OWNER = F.OWNER_ID WHERE A.CUSTOMER_GROUP IS NOT NULL AND A.STATUS = 0 and A.CUSTOMER_GROUP <> '*None' AND E.SHIP_DATE BETWEEN (SELECT MONTH_BEGIN_DATE FROM dbo.FISCAL_MONTH_CALENDAR WITH (nolock) WHERE SYSDATETIME() BETWEEN MONTH_BEGIN_DATE AND MONTH_END_DATE) AND (SELECT MONTH_END_DATE FROM dbo.FISCAL_MONTH_CALENDAR WITH (nolock) WHERE DATEADD(month,2,SYSDATETIME())BETWEEN MONTH_BEGIN_DATE AND MONTH_END_DATE)

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: To generate demand driver based on item_code
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_FINISHED_PRODUCT_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT LTRIM(RTRIM(FINISHED_PRODUCT_ITEM.ITEM_CODE)) as ITEM_CODE, FINISHED_PRODUCT_ITEM.DEMAND_DRIVER as DEMAND_DRIVER FROM FINISHED_PRODUCT_ITEM WITH (NOLOCK)

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup CUSTOMER_EVENT_GROUP to get the Customer_Event_Group.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_EDM_CUST_EVENT_GRP

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT CUSTOMER_EVENT_GROUP .Customer_Event_Group as Customer_Event_Group, CUSTOMER_EVENT_GROUP .Customer_Event_Group_ID as Customer_Event_Group_ID FROM CUSTOMER_EVENT_GROUP WITH (NOLOCK)

TRANSFORMATION.NAME: AGG_OPEN_ORD_SUM

TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_PREPACK_DIM_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT PREPACK_COMP_XREF.AF_GRID as AF_GRID, PREPACK_COMP_XREF.MATERIAL as MATERIAL, PREPACK_COMP_XREF.COMPONENT as COMPONENT, PREPACK_COMP_XREF.ZCMP_GRID as ZCMP_GRID, PREPACK_COMP_XREF.COMPITEMID as COMPITEMID, MAX(PREPACK_COMP_XREF.PLANT) as PLANT, PREPACK_COMP_XREF.ZCOMP_QTY as ZCOMP_QTY, PREPACK_COMP_XREF.ZITEMID as ZITEMID FROM PREPACK_COMP_XREF GROUP BY PREPACK_COMP_XREF.AF_GRID, PREPACK_COMP_XREF.MATERIAL, PREPACK_COMP_XREF.COMPONENT, PREPACK_COMP_XREF.ZCMP_GRID, PREPACK_COMP_XREF.COMPITEMID, PREPACK_COMP_XREF.ZCOMP_QTY, PREPACK_COMP_XREF.ZITEMID

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: SQ is used to extract the required fields from Source using override query.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT Dim_Item.Style_Num, Dim_Item.Color_Code, Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi.Rejected_Qty, Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi.Order_Qty, Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi.Invoice_Qty, Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi.Open_Qty, Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi.Allocation_Qty, Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi.Delivered_Qty, Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi.Sold_To , Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi.Dim_Customer_ID,Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi.Dim_Item_ID, Fiscal_Mth FROM ( SELECT Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi.Dim_Item_ID,Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi.Rejected_Qty, Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi.Order_Qty, Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi.Invoice_Qty, Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi.Open_Qty, Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi.Allocation_Qty, Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi.Delivered_Qty, Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi.Sold_To, Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi.Dim_Customer_ID, Dim_Week.Fiscal_Mth Fiscal_Mth FROM SLM.dbo.Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi with (nolock) JOIN Dim_Time with (nolock) ON FACT_BOOK_SHIP_SAPBI.Requested_Ship_Date = Dim_Time.Day_Date_Int JOIN dbo.Dim_Week Dim_Week with (nolock) ON Dim_Week.AS_of_Date_INT = Dim_Time.AS_of_Date_INT WHERE Dim_Week.Fiscal_Mth IN (select distinct Fiscal_Mth from dbo.Dim_Week a with (nolock) left join dbo.Dim_Time b with (nolock) on a.AS_of_Date_INT = b.As_of_Date_int where b.Day_Date_int BETWEEN convert(int,convert(varchar,GETDATE(),112),112) and convert(int,convert(varchar,dateadd(month,2,GETDATE()),112),112)) and (Header_Rej_cd IN ('ZD', 'ZX')or Header_Rej_cd IS NULL) and (Item_Rej_cd IN ('ZD', 'ZX') or Item_Rej_cd is NULL) and upper(Order_Doc_Type) IN ('Z000','Z020','Z210','Z300') )Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi join (select Dim_Item.Style_Num, Dim_Item.Color_Code, Dim_Item.Color_Name, Dim_Item.SAP_Wholesale_Price, Dim_Item_ID from Dim_Item with (nolock) Join Dim_Style with (nolock) on Dim_Item.Dim_Style_ID = Dim_Style.Dim_Style_ID)DIM_ITEM on DIM_ITEM.Dim_Item_ID=Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi.Dim_Item_ID order by Fact_Book_Ship_Sapbi.Sold_To

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup Transformation on XRF_ACC table

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT A.CUST_EVENT_GRP_ID as CUST_EVENT_GRP_ID, A.TS_DIV_CDE as TS_DIV_CDE, CASE WHEN SUBSTR(A.xrf_account,1,3)='TSP' and ts_Div_Cde <> 'SP' THEN trim(A.soldto) ELSE nvl(ltrim(A.Soldto, '0'), 'UNMAPPED') END AS SOLDTO FROM XRF_ACC A WHERE A.CUST_SEQ_NBR IN ( SELECT MAX(B.CUST_SEQ_NBR) AS CUST_SEQ_NBR FROM XRF_ACC B where A.Soldto=B.Soldto And A.TS_DIV_CDE= B.TS_DIV_CDE)

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT A.Ts_Div_Code as Ts_Div_Code, A.Soldto as Soldto, A.Dim_Customer_ID as Dim_Customer_ID FROM Dim_Customer A with (nolock) where A.Customer_Seq_Num in( select Max(Customer_Seq_Num) from Dim_Customer B with (nolock) where A.Ts_Div_Code=B.Ts_Div_Code and A.Soldto=B.Soldto )
